# Mirroring guide

Prerequisites:
* Linux server
* Installed git and go (on Ubuntu the package is called `golang-go`)

Steps:
1. Log into the server using ssh
2. Do these commands:

  mkdir -p bin
  git clone https://github.com/aajonusonline/aajonus.online
  cd aajonus.online
  go mod tidy
  go build -o ~/bin/srv ./server
  sudo sh -c '~/bin/srv -p 8080 >> ~/server.log 2>&1 &'

3. Sometimes check for updates by doing this:

  cd aajonus.online
  git pull

4. If there was an update, server needs to be restarted with:

  sudo pkill srv
  cd aajonus.online
  go mod tidy
  go build -o ~/bin/srv ./server
  sudo sh -c '~/bin/srv -p 8080 >> ~/server.log 2>&1 &'
